---
title: Chicken Pineapple Quesadillas with Pico de Gallo & Southwest Spice
description: If you think sweet-and-savory combos are amazing, prepare to be blown away by this Tex-Mex creation. Chicken and shredded mozzarella bring the classic comforts you crave, while our Southwest spice blend adds some smoky warmth. But any notions you might have about quesadillas go out the window when the pineapple comes to shake things up in the most delicious way.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-pineapple-quesadillas-8b9f1f15.jpg
